And while we were off air, the three of us had a bit of an argument

00:42.240 --> 00:47.120
about what would be the best car to take on a Grand Tour of Europe.

00:47.120 --> 00:48.800
I reckon, and I'm right,

00:48.800 --> 00:51.860
it's the Aston Martin DBS Volante.

