07:11.230 --> 07:13.840
'Then we did what we weren't supposed to do.'

07:14.520 --> 07:18.780
In 3, 2, 1, go!

07:20.800 --> 07:22.590
Oh, yeah, this is what we mustn't do.

07:31.180 --> 07:33.930
It just has the legs, that Ferrari.

07:34.940 --> 07:37.250
Just, just, just.

07:37.250 --> 07:39.810
Yeah, this might be a GT car,but it's...

07:40.640 --> 07:41.900
It's not a slouch.

07:42.850 --> 07:45.850
Aston Martin has gone to simply enormous lengths

07:46.510 --> 07:48.850
to make the DVS convertible as light as possible.

07:48.850 --> 07:51.110
It has a carbon-fibre bonnet,

07:51.110 --> 07:52.310
carbon-fibre wings,

07:52.310 --> 07:53.810
carbon-fibre boot,

07:53.810 --> 07:55.740
carbon-fibre door-pulls, even.

